^ PR Newswire Morningstar Names Bruce Berkowitz, David Herro, and Bill Gross Fund Managers of the Decade
^ The Jewish Businessman Who Beats Warren Buffett At His Own Game. 19 July 2009
^ Forbes: "Bruce Berkowitz Dances Quietly to the Beat of His Own Investment Drum" November 20, 2014
^ Times of Israel: "The Jewish Origins of Value investing" by Gabriele Grego December 8, 2014
^ a b c d Chelsea Record: "A real Chelsea success story" 15 July 2010
^ Cendrowski, Scott (December 10, 2010). "Bruce Berkowitz: the megamind of Miami". Fortune. 
^ a b Fortune Bruce Berkowitz: The megamind of Miami
^ Fortune
^ The Jewish Week: "History Center In The Black" by Tamar Snyder 25 January 2011



